# Solution: rust_web_social_expert_073_cross_file_refactoring_expert_01

## Key Files Identified

- /app/project/src/module_15.txt - Badge awarding micro-service with `Dispatcher` struct for event publishing via broadcast channel
- /app/project/src/module_48.txt - Outbox → Broker integration with `EventPublisher` trait and `NatsPublisher` implementation
- /app/project/src/module_77.txt - Outbox & Domain-Event infrastructure with `EventPublisher` trait and `StdoutPublisher` mock
- /app/project/src/utils.txt - Utility helpers module that needs `event_bus` submodule with mock functions
- /app/project/src/event_publisher.txt - NEW FILE: Centralized event publishing service (to be created)

## Code Evidence

### Module 15 - Current Event Publishing Logic

